text: Yuliya Rytsikava (born September 8, 1986) is a Belarusian basketball player. She represented Belarus in the basketball competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian women's basketball players Category:Olympic basketball players of Belarus Category:Basketball players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Shooting guards Category:People from Smarhon’
